id":"eed3c6aa8d0133fbc658574ee4154417d8a29ac7","tid":408591,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Carlill v Carbolic Smoke Ball Co</blockquote><br />\n原審無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原審係邊個?<br />\n<br />\n生蕃咁</blockquote><br />\n咪係，個個第一日讀law就要識呢條金科玉律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a2b8d1c47f686d43e4fe4c2149e2b1244ac859","tid":408591,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"想知係咪被告自己出錢 上訴推翻的？<br />\n因為如果冇錢比堂費，咁就一世案底，多得條on鳩唔少。"}]}